<main role="main">
    <div class="album py-3 bg-light">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">

                <div class="col-md-3 project-detail-sb">
                    <div class="sb-links ">
                        <h2>links</h2>
                        <div>
                            <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#">Live Demo</a>
                        </div>
                        <div class="my-2">
                            <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="#">GitHub URL</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="sb-links mb-2">
                        <h2>Tags</h2>
                        <div class="my-2">
                            {{#each project.tags}}
                                <a class="badge badge-{{this.class}}" href="#">{{this.name}}</a>
                            {{/each}}
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="sb-links mb-2">
                        <h2>Related projects</h2>
                        {{#each project.relatedProjects}}
                            <div class="my-2">
                                <a href="/projects/{{this.link}}">{{this.name}}</a>
                            </div>
                        {{/each}}
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-md-9">
                    <nav aria-label="breadcrumb">
                        <ol class="breadcrumb">
                            <li class="breadcrumb-item"><a href="#">Home</a></li>
                            <li class="breadcrumb-item"><a href="#">Projects</a></li>
                            <li class="breadcrumb-item active" aria-current="page">{{project.alias}}</li>

                        </ol>
                    </nav>
                    <h2>{{project.name}}</h2>
                    <p>In this project you will build a small number guessing game. System will select a random number between 1 and 100. See if you can guess it in 10 turns or fewer. We'll tell you if your guess was too high or too low</p>
                    

                    <img src="/images/image1.png" width="200" height="200" alt={{project.alias}} />

                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</main>